-- Rothschild Gestion New Branch Targets Swiss Institutions, La Tribune Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-08T04:43:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/rothschild-gestion-new-branch-targets-swiss-institutions-la-tribune-says.html

          
          
             Rothschild & Cie Gestion is opening a
branch in Zurich to target institutions, French daily La Tribune
reported, citing the company.  
 The branch will be managed by Konstantin Nikiteas, the
newspaper said. Rothschild & Cie Gestion may also expand into
Scandinavia and Italy next year, La Tribune said.  
          
          


  


        